title: Miners win to tie series against LA Tech - The Prospector
content: Miners win to tie series against LA Tech  The Prospector
description: The UTEP softball team (11-8, 2-7) got a victory against Louisiana Tech University (19-12, 4-3) March 26 at the Helen of Troy Softball Complex. The Miners were able to  get in some good hits and drive in runs consistently.   In the beginning of the first inning, junior pitcher Isabella Kelly only allowed one hit...
